### Test Check-in/Check-out API
### Requires: REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/checkin-checkout
@contractServiceUrl = http://localhost:5001/api

### 1. Get Pending Check-ins
GET {{baseUrl}}/pending-checkins
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get Pending Check-outs
GET {{baseUrl}}/pending-checkouts
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get All Check-ins
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkins
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get All Check-outs
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkouts
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Get Check-in by Contract ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkin/contract/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Get Check-out by Contract ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkout/contract/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Create Check-in
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contractId": 1,
  "studentId": 1,
  "roomId": 1,
  "roomNumber": "101",
  "buildingName": "Tòa A",
  "checkInDate": "2026-06-14T10:00:00Z",
  "checkedInByUserId": 1,
  "checkedInByName": "Admin",
  "idCardImageUrls": "[\"http://example.com/id1.jpg\", \"http://example.com/id2.jpg\"]",
  "isDepositPaid": true,
  "depositAmount": 1000000,
  "depositPaidAt": "2026-06-14T10:00:00Z",
  "roomConditionChecklist": "[\"walls\", \"doors\", \"electric\", \"water\", \"furniture\", \"clean\"]",
  "roomImageUrls": "[\"http://example.com/room1.jpg\", \"http://example.com/room2.jpg\"]",
  "roomCondition": "Good",
  "notes": "Phòng sạch sẽ, đầy đủ nội thất",
  "initialElectricityReading": 100.5,
  "initialWaterReading": 50.2,
  "keysProvided": "1 chìa khóa phòng + 1 thẻ từ",
  "keyCount": 2
}

###

### 8. Create Check-out
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contractId": 1,
  "studentId": 1,
  "roomId": 1,
  "roomNumber": "101",
  "buildingName": "Tòa A",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-12-14T10:00:00Z",
  "checkedOutByUserId": 1,
  "checkedOutByName": "Admin",
  "currentRoomImageUrls": "[\"http://example.com/checkout1.jpg\", \"http://example.com/checkout2.jpg\"]",
  "roomCondition": "Good",
  "damageDescription": null,
  "depositAmount": 1000000,
  "compensationCost": 0,
  "refundAmount": 1000000,
  "compensationDetails": null,
  "finalElectricityReading": 150.8,
  "finalWaterReading": 75.6,
  "isKeyReturned": true,
  "isDepositRefunded": true,
  "depositRefundedAt": "2026-12-14T10:00:00Z",
  "refundMethod": "Cash",
  "notes": "Phòng sạch sẽ, không hư hỏng"
}

###

### 9. Create Check-out with Damage
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contractId": 2,
  "studentId": 2,
  "roomId": 2,
  "roomNumber": "102",
  "buildingName": "Tòa A",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-12-14T10:00:00Z",
  "checkedOutByUserId": 1,
  "checkedOutByName": "Admin",
  "currentRoomImageUrls": "[\"http://example.com/damage1.jpg\", \"http://example.com/damage2.jpg\"]",
  "roomCondition": "Minor",
  "damageDescription": "Tường bị trầy xước, bàn bị vỡ một góc",
  "depositAmount": 1000000,
  "compensationCost": 200000,
  "refundAmount": 800000,
  "compensationDetails": "Sửa tường: 100,000 VND, Thay bàn: 100,000 VND",
  "finalElectricityReading": 145.3,
  "finalWaterReading": 72.1,
  "isKeyReturned": true,
  "isDepositRefunded": true,
  "depositRefundedAt": "2026-12-14T10:00:00Z",
  "refundMethod": "BankTransfer",
  "refundReference": "TF20261214001",
  "notes": "Đã khấu trừ 200,000 VND để sửa chữa"
}

###

### Helper: Get All Contracts (to check status updates)
GET {{contractServiceUrl}}/Contracts
Accept: application/json

###

### Helper: Get Contract by ID
GET {{contractServiceUrl}}/Contracts/1
Accept: application/json

###
